title: MNF and Week 6 Recap
description:
The team breaks down the MNF clash between the Broncos and the Chargers. The group also dives into Aaron Rodgers and the Packer's offensive miscues, as well as Quinnen Williams and the Jets' defensive success. On another edition of Touchscreen Tuesday, Dan and RC break down Russell Wilson's recent play, and the team gives all the latest news from the day.
